reviewText: I bought this tape when it was new so it was a lot cheaper. The Dodgers were the better team in 1977 and 1978 against the Yankees and revenge time came in 1981 when the Dodgers came back from an 0-2 deficit to kick New York off it's self-serving pedestal.  Steve Garvey, Steve Yeager, Pedro Guerrero, Ron Cey and the rest of this group just refused to lose.  Go Blue!
